item.title: CVE-2018-1933|2024-08-05T04:14:39.269Z -- ibm -- planning%20analytics
item.description: IBM Planning Analytics 2.0 through 2.0.6 is vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 153177.
